{"tid":785502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃錦星指「四電一腦」計劃運作大致暢順","createTime":"2018-08-19T09:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T10:19:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5675216e8b62535d6d6a16f7292bb23b6bf4390b","tid":785502,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"環境局局長黃錦星表示，業界反映「四電一腦」生產者責任計劃運作大致暢順，前線員工及顧客開始適應新法例，達至預期效果。<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星指，目前有三間回收商持有可拆解電器的廢物處置牌照，而大部分零售商及供應商已完成除舊批註及相關登記程序。<br />\n<br />\n被問到唐樓住戶透過指定回收商回收電器時，是否需要自行將電器搬至地下，黃錦星表示，在這情況下，指定回收商都有責任到戶收集電器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1413281-20180819.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1413281-20180819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xQ9dSepvmkXJdIl2SX%2B4mkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d6ca3065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1413281-20180819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=32389b4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1413281-20180819.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"cac89ddd80ae7a53886c1437ef9b6daaee8bbdbf","tid":785502,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"佢平時日日痾爛屎都會話痾得好暢順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af37e5065eb978dbc67f0986a17ee4ac9dffd78","tid":785502,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"扔哂岀街之嘛&hellip;"},{"pid":"86b738f65344ff227e5499e5e1611cbc5a953a62","tid":785502,"uid":19141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"預期效果=無人理個回收商照搬去垃圾站，回收商唔洗做野又收到錢，成功做到利益輸送"},{"pid":"9145739c1223805ca4d0d27831f29552f274ab4d","tid":785502,"uid":48973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"以為佢只係冇頭髮，原來個殼都係空"},{"pid":"8efebb443e690bb1e0abb50021a6ad869db99678","tid":785502,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"你地落街見到好多電器咩 我覺得香港行環保唔計俾地產商綁架既土地議題幾務實<br />\n<br />\n好似膠袋收費明明所有數據都證明成功 但班弱智仔都係要踩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}